node.text: Halston was a little sad that she didn’t go to school too yesterday. She had her backpack on all ready and I had to break the news to her. BUT her and I spent hours riding bikes and stopping at all the parks. She’s so sweet and cute. Being a mom is so fun ❤️ she’s my little bestie. The conversations we have when we ride bikes together is so cute!!!!! Kids say the best things. Love getting new twinning outfits too! These are from @sunpeonycoconut 💚

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by MADISON FISHER on August 25, 2021 tagging @taytumandoakley. May be an image of 3 people, child and people standing.

node.text: This was the best day ever! Taytum and Oakley started KINDERGARTEN!! After the LONGEST year of staying at home/ preschool being shut down, these girls could not WAIT to start school. I’m happiest knowing my kids are learning & thriving! Guess what I did?🤣 I was that annoying mom that literally rode by their school on my bike and hid to see them at recess🤣 I just was so excited!!! They loved their classes & teachers! I can’t wait for them to make friends and then I can set up play dates ! 🥳 And I signed up to help for their class parties! I’m so into this! 🍎 📚

node.text: Which outfit is your favorite?! I put together some fall outfits from @pinklily ! Get 20% off with discount code MadisonB20 🍁 I’m SO excited for the fall because I now live in a state that realllly changes seasons ! Ahhhh! Can’t wait. 🍁 🍂 #pinklilystyle #pinklily

node.text: Last week of summer break until these cuties start Kindergarten!! 😍 I’m actually really excited for them. I requested for them to be in separate classes because I really think it will help them thrive! My girls are really attached to each other & they tend to rely on each other’s approval before making decisions. Most of the time, Taytum takes on the leadership role and I can tell that Oakley sometimes can feel it. So I think that this will be amazzzzingg for them. Taytum and Oakley LOVE to learn, they have Been asking when school starts for months now. I cannot wait for next week!👏🏼
